sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant J as Jito Block Engine
    participant S as Stream Tracker
    participant F as Failure Classifier
    participant A as AI Retry Agent
    participant B as Blockhash Manager
    participant T as Tip Estimator

    O->>J: sendBundle
    J-->>O: bundle_id
    S-->>O: no processed/confirmed/finalized progression
    O->>F: classify timeout/status/error
    F-->>A: expired_blockhash or fee_too_low or leader_skipped
    A->>B: refresh blockhash if needed
    A->>T: reprice tip if needed
    A-->>O: retry/hold/abort decision
    O->>J: resubmit rebuilt bundle
